room_title: Escape room "Dinner Party" by Brainstorm Escape Room Bonita Springs in Fort Myers
room_description: A co-worker invites you and your friends over for dinner and drinks. After a few drinks and a few laughs, you and your friends blackout! As you slowly wake up, you find yourselves locked in! Your adrenaline rushes as you see a timer counting down. You only have 60 minutes left! Do you think you've got what it takes to escape the room before the psycho comes back?
